summary: The document is a classified communication dated 13 November 1963, marked 'SECRET', and related to the President John F. Kennedy Assassination Records Act of 1992. It requests provisional operational approval and references materials under separate cover, including a subject's cryptonym assigned in October 1965 by the station. The document includes distribution instructions and a headquarters file number, potentially pertaining to events surrounding the Kennedy assassination.
key_findings: The document is part of the records released under the President John F. Kennedy Assassination Records Act of 1992.
It requests provisional operational approval and references materials related to a subject with a cryptonym assigned in 1965.
The document is classified as 'SECRET' and includes a headquarters file number.
Dated 13 November 1963, it may pertain to events surrounding the Kennedy assassination.
